Prerequisites  Complete the Setup  Payment Failures Navigate to MuShop application at http://localhost:8000 if using kubectl port-forward as discussed under Setup and add items to cart to exceed the amount greater than $105 and PLACE ORDER. The request will be denied with HTTP 406 &ldquo;Request Not Acceptable&rdquo;
Click on PLACE ORDER 9-10 times just to create some additional failure log data.
Observe Navigate to OCI Console Monitoring -&gt; Metrics Explorer
